  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault项目画一个思维导图，梳理一下它的核心脉络。我觉得可以从起源、研究、工具三个维度展开，你觉得这个结构怎么样？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "Origins",
        "Research",
        "Tools"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个主干分支：起源、研究、工具。我先把这个根节点和三个一级分支搭起来，结构清晰，后续再细化内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "Origins",
        "Research",
        "Tools"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好。在起源这边，我想强调它有很长的历史积淀，不是突然冒出来的概念。研究这块要放两个方向：一个是有效性研究，另一个是自动创建的机制研究。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Origins",
        "Long history",
        "Research",
        "On effectiveness",
        "On Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经加上了——起源下面挂了\"Long history\"，研究下面拆成\"On effectiveness\"和\"On Automatic creation\"两条。工具分支目前是空的，你打算放什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Long history",
        "On effectiveness",
        "On Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "工具部分我想对比传统和现代两种。先放最基础的纸笔，然后是我们现在用的Mermaid，这样形成反差，突出技术演进。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Tools",
        "Pen and paper",
        "Mermaid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，纸笔和Mermaid作为工具分支的两个子节点。我检查一下整体结构：根节点HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，下面起源、研究、工具三大块，各自有对应的内容，层级都是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "Pen and paper",
        "Mermaid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，研究那里的\"On Automatic creation\"我想确认一下表述——原文其实是想表达\"自动化创建\"这个研究方向，你写的是\"Automatic\"还是\"Auto\"？我需要确保和内部文档一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "On Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我写的是\"On Automatic creation\"，用的是完整单词Automatic。如果内部文档是简写Auto，我可以马上调整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "On Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改，完整单词是对的，我刚才记混了。Automatic creation保持现状就好。整个图结构完整了，可以定稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "On Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，最终版本已确认。根节点HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，三层结构：起源含历史、研究含有效性与自动创建、工具含纸笔和Mermaid。导图完成。",
